4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp aimed at individuals interested in launching a career in cybersecurity without prior experience. Over 16 weeks, students will attend three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. The curriculum includes foundational knowledge in Windows and Linux, network and server administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat analysis. The course is presented in English or Spanish, with an official completion certificate awarded at the end. The median salary for cybersecurity professionals in the U.S. is approximately $103,560. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop